-- Kumba Would Consider `Value Sharing' at Its Sishen Mine, Business Day Says
-- Antony Sguazzin
-- 2010-07-27T04:39:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-27/kumba-would-consider-value-sharing-at-its-sishen-mine-business-day-says.html

          
          
             Anglo American Plc’s Kumba Iron Ore
Ltd. may consider “value sharing” if it wins arbitration over
a disputed minority stake in mining rights at its Sishen mine in
South Africa, Business Day said, citing an unidentified
spokesman from the company.  
          
          


  


        